platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Zipping down snowy hills, trying to stay ahead of a massive avalanchethe pressures always on in this infinite-racing classic. And we love that whirlwind pace, fueled by landing backflips and hitching rides on penguins, snowmobiles, and yetis. From the games masterful one-touch controls to its cheery music, every aspect feels perfectly tuned to keep you playing through long afternoons and late nights.
